nding site 有大量carboxylate groups<br />\n而ionic nature of RE 令到佢prefer O donor (Oxophilicity）<br />\n而佢既unique local coordinations environment<br />\n導致到RE 有strong affinity towards metalloprotein<br />\n可以exclude 其他trivalent ions/divalent ions<br />\n換佢話講 姐係呢隻baterical係專係用嚟<br />\n吸hard Ln3+ 而呢d metal ions 通常都較難accumulates 係human body <br />\n而住住導致heavy metal poisoning 既metal係岩岩相反 通常都係soft metal (e,g Hg, Ag) prefer soft donor (S, C) 所以似乎呢隻菌反而唔係咁岩駛"},{"pid":"84616c84207aced811b0a1552aa6cc953be2ca5d","tid":2184760,"uid":253444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"LM 學嘢"}]}